##
## Upstream tests to disable on Windows ASAN builds only
##
## When adding a new filter to this list, please include a short description of
## why the filter is required and create an associated tracking issue.
##

# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/53717
# Flaky on Windows x64 ASAN. ManifestSilentUpdateCommand queues a background
# GetData() task whose FinishAndStartNextTask cleanup may still be pending when
# HasCurrent() is asserted. Upstream flake rate 0.6% (LUCI Analysis, 30 days).
# No Brave modifications to installable manager code path.
-InstallableManagerBrowserTest.CheckWebapp
